data.title: Community Foundation Donors
data.meta_description: Donors giving to the Community Foundation provide unrestricted gifts used where they are most critically needed, as well as gifts to our various initiatives.
data.text:
Thank You to Our Park City Community Foundation Donors

These many generous supporters have contributed to our Annual Community Fund, Early Childhood Fund, Mental Wellness Fund, Park City Climate Fund, Solomon Fund, RISE Fund, and our Endowment. From meeting current challenges to supporting innovative solutions, local nonprofits enrich the community. Together, this is accomplished with the generosity of our donors. Thank you.
